{"tid":379212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你有筆loan 會唔會借比你屋企人","createTime":"2017-08-29T06:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:51:10.000Z","uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04a23f8e4c3f24b10136c81043b33ca63e829dcf","tid":379212,"uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"話說我屋企都幾窮 不過我哥長期係外國讀書 但係其實屋企人比好小錢佢(返小一個月工連食都有困難)<br />\n<br />\n佢讀埋下年就grad, 咁細佬我岩岩讀college 有筆40000$ hkd 既loan 應唔應該借晒比大佬頂住先無咁辛苦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c91ea198d4aef28753dfc4fbfacf6c4d76e673e","tid":379212,"uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"求屌醒"},{"pid":"a0bafcf38a5c9efd10cb9ab3c7aa439f0984e3f3","tid":379212,"uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd37c61aef834f3c88c7d660a8c07186c668ff5d","tid":379212,"uid":66438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"你細佬同你呀哥關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf50fd42cfdbff01a1cb94cfaf17966ddc20fd6","tid":379212,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"感情好就借啦<br />\n唔駛問人<br />\n我都借咗幾皮嘢畀啊哥開舖"},{"pid":"fff2e972733856cf8e57b2293b8d683e83be5e94","tid":379212,"uid":73785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"你借左咪你辛苦"},{"pid":"00656a93c8d2ad31647f34ffc6b441520f2aa6e1","tid":379212,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"借埋你個屎忽loan"},{"pid":"6931ea6d8ad8120fa8c0542e1bc337164afab44d","tid":379212,"uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你細佬同你呀哥關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif