>\n除非有身分</blockquote><br />\n係 有身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國肯認真搵份工都夠生活....仲要有身分搵工話咁易<br />\n洗咩你幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99764efd189396e29d8ef5c8fd1b2802d0a2c23","tid":379212,"uid":22000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>窮但係有錢去美國讀書<br />\n玩咩<br />\n除非有身分</blockquote><br />\n係 有身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國肯認真搵份工都夠生活....仲要有身分搵工話咁易<br />\n洗咩你幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無講清楚sor <br />\n係我全家係美國 得佢一個係香港 所以先講外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}